    %section
      %h2 Application Process, Dates, & Deadlines
      %p Each session is preceded by a Meet & Greet, an informal get together where you can chat with current students, meet our instructor, and ask all your burning questions.
      %p
        During the weeks preceding the application deadline, we offer application help sessions at the Portland Ruby
        %a{:href => "http://calagator.org/events/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&query=hack%2Bhelp"} Hack + Help Meetup
      %p Notifications of acceptance will go out at least two weeks prior to the start of the session. Applications are being accepted for 2013 Summer and Fall Sessions, please indicate which session you are applying for.

