    %section
      %h2 Key Application Criteria
      %p We want to get to know you as a person as well as a programmer. In order to ensure our graduates can succeed in web development careers, we look for evidence that you are well rounded, creative, and are able to engage in the whole programming experience, not just the technical aspects.
      %p When we review your application, we will be looking for evidence that:
      %ul
        %li You are passionate about programming above all other things
        %li You can and want to learn about programming
        %li You can get along with other students and future co-workers
      %p If you have questions about application materials or the application process, send us an email or give us a call!
